es ont \u00e9t\u00e9 remploy\u00e9es touts par Chretien Gottlieb Stiehl \u00e0 Dresde (...) imprim\u00e9 \u00e0 Copenhague chez Martin Hallagger, 1775\u0022. \r\nSeul le revers du couvercle n\u0027est pas doubl\u00e9 d\u0027or.","inscriptions":"Poin\u00e7on : \r ; Titre 750 (Poin\u00e7on de garantie et de charge, France, Division du Nord (1819 - 1838) : gorge \u00e0 droite)\r ; (Marque illisible : gorge \u00e0 droite)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"3,9","displayDimension":"3,9 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Longueur","value":"8,4","displayDimension":"8,4 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"6,2","displayDimension":"6,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : or\r\nMat\u00e9riau : pierre (pierres dures diverses)","placeOfCreation":"Dresde (Allemagne-\u003ESaxe)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection Philippe Lenoir ; legs M. et Mme Philippe Lenoir, 1874","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"M. Lenoir, Philippe Balthazard Marin","note":"","role":", Collectionneur ; Donateur"},{"value":"Mme Lenoir, Marie-Aspasie","note":"","role":", Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"legs","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date","value":"1874","startYear":1874,"endYear":1874}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"legs"}],"period":[{"value":"Louis XVI (1774-1792)"}],"place":[{"value":"Dresde"}],"objectType":[{"value":"accessoire personnel, bo\u00eete, \u00e9tui"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Louvre couture - Objets d\u0027art, o